            <title>[LUCENE-2597] Query scorers should not use MultiFields</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2597</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Lucene does all searching/filtering per-segment, today, but there are a number of tests that directly invoke Scorer.scorer or Filter.getDocIdSet on a composite reader.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
