                    <comment id="12897321" author="mikemccand" created="Wed, 11 Aug 2010 17:00:32 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Only a few query impls were affected, but many tests were directly passing composite readers to the low level API.  I added a new helper class SlowMultiReaderWrapper that one can use to wrap an existing composite reader to make it &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;inefficiently&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; pretend it&apos;s an atomic reader.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
